emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of 1957 Alpha Kappa Alpha Debutantes including possibly Barbara Charles standing in center, gathered around table in interior
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. 10 reads: "AKA Debs - Preparing to make their bow Penn-Sheraton Hotel, May 18, under the auspices of Alpha Kappa Alpha sorority, are these charming young ladies...Irene Harper, Patricia Mann, Myra Eddins, Maureen Avery, Maxine Brown, Barbara Charles, and Joan Stotts."
